## Infraestructura Docker

Dos servicios nuevos en `docker-compose.yml`:

### `opensearch`

| Parámetro | Valor |
|-----------|-------|
| Imagen | `opensearchproject/opensearch:2.13.0` |
| Modo | `single-node` |
| Seguridad | `plugins.security.disabled=true` |
| JVM heap | `-Xms512m -Xmx512m` |
| Puerto externo | `${OPENSEARCH_PORT:-9200}:9200` |
| Volumen | `opensearch_data:/usr/share/opensearch/data` |
| Healthcheck | `curl -f http://localhost:9200/_cluster/health` |
| start_period | 60s (OpenSearch tarda en iniciar) |
| ulimits | `memlock: -1/-1`, `nofile: 65536/65536` |

### `opensearch-dashboards`

| Parámetro | Valor |
|-----------|-------|
| Imagen | `opensearchproject/opensearch-dashboards:2.13.0` |
| Puerto externo | `${OPENSEARCH_DASHBOARDS_PORT:-5601}:5601` |
| Env | `OPENSEARCH_HOSTS=http://opensearch:9200` |
| Env | `DISABLE_SECURITY_DASHBOARDS_PLUGIN=true` |
| depends_on | `opensearch (service_healthy)` |

Volumen nuevo: `opensearch_data:`

