## Orden de implementación

1. `docker-compose.yml` — infraestructura primero
2. `composer require opensearch-project/opensearch-php:^2.0` (Laravel)
3. `OpenSearchHandler.php` + `OpenSearchChannel.php` (Laravel)
4. `config/logging.php` — registrar canal y cambiar default
5. `backend/.env.example` — variables de entorno
6. `npm install @opensearch-project/opensearch` en `services/socketio/`
7. Modificar `services/socketio/src/logger.ts` — añadir `OpenSearchTransport`
8. `make/dev.mk` + `docs/stages/01-infra.mdc` — DX y documentación

